Before you start planning, you can have a look at the `README.md` file inside of project so you can have a brief picture of functionality it already has
After finishing a task, run a smoke test in a browser using Cursor tools.
After creating a new feature for the project, don't forget to document only important information about it in `README.md` file. Include only features, not bugfixes or "best practices" info. Make it concise and short.
